text: "Wiggle" is a 2014 song by American singer Jason Derulo featuring American rapper Snoop Dogg and is taken from his albums Tattoos and Talk Dirty. It peaked at number 5 on the US Billboard Hot 100 and peaked at number 8 in the United Kingdom. It went to the top 10 in Australia, Austria, Belgium, the Czech Republic, Denmark, France, Germany, Hungary, Ireland, Lebanon, the Netherlands, New Zealand, Norway, Scotland, Slovakia, South Africa, Sweden and Switzerland. == References == Category:2014 songs Category:Jason Derulo songs Category:Snoop Dogg songs
